title: Stars wear famous faces
text: Blogs Stars wear famous faces They may be famous, but that doesn't stop celebrities from idolizing their favorite stars! Check out these celebs wearing other famous faces. Photo: sarahfuckingsnyder via Instagram, Getty Images./ Published: 10/2/2015 1:32:59 Sarah Snyder It doesn't look like Jaden Smith's girlfriend is going to win over his parents Will and Jada Pinkett Smith with this look! The 19-year-old model donned a t-shirt featuring her mugshot to her court hearing on Sept. 30, 2015. "56 nights," Snyder captioned the Instagram snap of herself donning the controversial Tee, referring to Future's song by the same name. Snyder appeared in court in New York after she was arrested back on June 15 for allegedly stealing a $15,995 Hermes bag. 1 of 22
